                          -- PREAMBLE --

THIS INSTRUMENT is a commercially issued license, authored by IACONOUS
WORTHYSON under the 75th Avenue licensing framework, and merges into
itself the personal declaration of its author -- Elad David Levi -- set
out in Article II below. It is not the exclusive property of any work.
It is a governing instrument -- available to any inventor, developer, or
creator who acquires it -- to protect and govern the work named in the
Certificate of Issuance above.

The 75th Avenue License v3.0 carries the same philosophical foundation
as its parent instrument: that creative and technical works of genuine
novelty belong, first, to the people who can build with them without
extracting from them -- and are withheld, by default, from commercial
entities absent the license holder's express written permission. In
this issuance, the author of the LICENSE and the author of the WORK are
the same person, appearing under both a legal name and a chosen
designation; both are declared in Article II.

The Works governed by this specific issuance are defined by the holder
named in the Certificate of Issuance. Where the license holder is a
different person than the license author in some future issuance of
this framework, the license author -- IACONOUS WORTHYSON -- holds no
claim over those Works beyond the right to be named as the author of
this instrument.


========================================================================
              Article I -- The Declaration of Prior Art
========================================================================

S 1.1  This License, together with all public deposits of the Works
made by the license holder, constitutes a public disclosure of prior
art under applicable patent law. The publication date of each deposit
is evidence that the disclosed concepts existed prior to any
subsequently filed patent application reading upon them.

S 1.2  From the moment of first public deposit, the Works and all
concepts substantially described therein become unpatentable prior art.
Any patent claim that reads upon this disclosure is invalid by operation
of prior art law, regardless of filing date. This applies in full to the
projected diamond CVD fabrication-time combination described in the
Works -- UV-assisted growth, femtosecond-laser nucleation seeding, and
femtosecond-laser defect correction, combined -- and to the light-field
nucleation models and their calibration against real glycine NPLIN data,
including the honest negative result of that calibration.

S 1.3  This declaration is the constitutional foundation of this
License. All other provisions rest upon it. It cannot be waived,
modified, or transferred by any party under any circumstance.

S 1.4  The license holder is strongly recommended to deposit their
Works to: Zenodo (CERN); OpenTimestamps (Bitcoin blockchain); and a
public GitHub repository. These three deposits form the strongest
available evidentiary record.


