  [X] AI TRAINING USE
      The Works, their models, source code, data, documentation, and
      any output produced by them may not be used as training data,
      fine-tuning data, evaluation data, or any form of machine
      learning corpus -- in whole or in part -- without a separately
      negotiated written instrument expressly authorising this use.

  [X] SURVEILLANCE
      The Works may not be used, directly or indirectly, to build,
      power, or enhance any system designed to monitor, track, profile,
      or surveil individuals without their knowledge and explicit
      ongoing consent.

  [X] DISINFORMATION AND MANIPULATION
      The Works may not be used to produce, distribute, or amplify
      false information; to manufacture synthetic media intended to
      deceive; or to build systems designed to psychologically
      manipulate individuals against their own interests. This
      includes misrepresenting the tested, negative light-field
      nucleation result as a positive one, or overstating the diamond
      CVD fabrication-time projection as a built or measured result.

  [X] PATENT FILING
      No license holder, licensee, permitted entity, contractor,
      partner, or successor may file any patent claim that reads upon
      the concepts, models, methods, or combinations of techniques
      disclosed in any Work under this License. Violation of this
      provision constitutes immediate and permanent termination of all
      rights under this issuance, without notice.


